Set cleaning pipeline
======================

Run set_cleaning pipeline

USAGE

nextflow run main.nf [OPTIONAL_ARGUMENTS] (--root)

DESCRIPTION

    --root_set=/path/to/[root_set]              Root folder containing multiple subjects

                                        [root]
                                        ├── S1
                                        │   └── F__Surface_Enhanced_Tractography/*.fib
                                        └── S2
                                            └── F__Surface_Enhanced_Tractography/*.fib

    --root_tractoflow=/path/to/[root_tractoflow] Root folder containing multiple subjects

                                        [root]
                                        ├── S1
                                        │   └── DTI_Metrics/*.nii.gz
                                        └── S2
                                            └── DTI_Metrics/*.nii.gz

    --output_dir                        Directory where to write the final results.
                                        By default, will be in "./results_set_conversion"

OPTIONAL ARGUMENTS (current value)

    --debug                             Debug will output more streamline files

AVAILABLE PROFILES (using -profile option (e.g. -profile macos))

macos When this profile is used, ExtractorFlow will modify a parameter (scratch) for MacOS users.
